'''喀麥隆英語區危機'''（{{lang-en|Anglophone Crisis}}，{{lang-fr|Crise anglophone}}），又稱'''亞巴佐尼亞戰爭'''<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.journalducameroun.com/en/ambazonia-war-drowns-sdf-28th-anniversary/|title= ‘Ambazonia War’ drowns SDF 28th Anniversary|publisher= Journal du Cameroun|date= 2018-05-28|accessdate= 2021-04-06|archive-date= 2018-10-25|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181025201919/https://www.journalducameroun.com/en/ambazonia-war-drowns-sdf-28th-anniversary/|dead-url= no}}</ref>或'''喀麥隆內戰'''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/10/06/world/africa/cameroon-election-biya-ambazonia.html|title=Cameroon on Brink of Civil War as English Speakers Recount ‘Unbearable’ Horrors|publisher=The New York Times|date=2018-10-06|accessdate=2021-04-06|archive-date=2019-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011111737/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/10/06/world/africa/cameroon-election-biya-ambazonia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[南喀麥隆|南喀麥隆]]{{le|喀麥隆英語區議題|Anglophone problem|英語區議題}}造成的武裝衝突<ref name=Africa>{{cite news|url=https://qz.com/1179202/cameroons-anglophone-crisis-is-threatening-to-spin-out-of-control/|title=Cameroon's Anglophone crisis is threatening to spin out of control|website=Quartz Africa|date=14 January 2018|access-date=22 April 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180531194152/https://qz.com/1179202/cameroons-anglophone-crisis-is-threatening-to-spin-out-of-control/|archive-date=2018-05-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[2016年－2017年喀麦隆抗议|2016年－2017年喀麦隆抗议]]後，主要講英語的南喀麥隆地區（[[西北區_(喀麥隆)|西北區]]與[[西南區_(喀麥隆)|西南區]]）武裝分子向喀麥隆軍隊發動攻擊，並宣布[[亞巴佐尼亞|亞巴佐尼亞]]恢復獨立，2017年底喀麥隆政府向分離主義者宣戰，派兵進入英語區<ref name=journal>{{cite news|url=https://www.journalducameroun.com/en/deadly-clashes-troops-adf-forces-leave-nguti-brink/|title=Deadly clashes between troops, ADF forces leave Nguti on the brink|website=Journal du Cameroun|date=13 March 2018|access-date=22 April 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421094808/https://www.journalducameroun.com/en/deadly-clashes-troops-adf-forces-leave-nguti-brink/|archive-date=2018-04-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

衝突在一年內散播到喀麥隆英語區全境，至2019年中，政府軍控制主要城市與部分鄉村，叛軍則控制部分鄉村，且有時在城市發動攻擊<ref name="crisisgroupmay22019"/>。2019年雙方一度{{tsl|en|Major National Dialogue|全國主要對話|展開談判}}<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.journalducameroun.com/en/cameroon-ambazonia-leaders-agree-to-participate-in-swiss-led-dialogue/|title= Cameroon: Ambazonia leaders endorse Swiss-led dialogue to solve Anglophone crisis|publisher= Journal du Cameroun|date= 2019-06-28|accessdate= 2021-04-06|archive-date= 2019-06-29|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190629234046/https://www.journalducameroun.com/en/cameroon-ambazonia-leaders-agree-to-participate-in-swiss-led-dialogue/|dead-url= no}}</ref>，並計劃給予英語區自治權<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-cameroon-separatists-lawmaking/cameroon-grants-special-status-to-anglophone-regions-idUSKBN1YO24S|title=Cameroon grants special status to Anglophone regions|publisher=Reuters|date=2019-12-20|accessdate=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126021833/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-cameroon-separatists-lawmaking/cameroon-grants-special-status-to-anglophone-regions-idUSKBN1YO24S|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但衝突仍持續擴大，{{tsl|en|2020 Cameroonian parliamentary election|2020年喀麥隆議會選舉}}期間政府向衝突地區增兵也再次激化了衝突，[[2019冠狀病毒病喀麥隆疫情|COVID-19疫情]]爆發後有一股叛軍單方面宣布為防疫而停火，但其他叛軍與政府軍仍持續交戰<ref name="voaapr92020">{{cite web|url=https://www.voanews.com/africa/cameroons-separatists-relaunch-attacks-reject-state-reconstruction-plan|title=Cameroon's Separatists Relaunch Attacks to Reject State Reconstruction Plan|publisher=Voice of America|date=2020-04-09|accessdate=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126034801/https://www.voanews.com/africa/cameroons-separatists-relaunch-attacks-reject-state-reconstruction-plan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年1月叛軍試圖阻止英語區城市[[林貝_(喀麥隆)|林貝]]舉辦{{tsl|en|2020 African Nations Championship|2020年非洲國家錦標賽|非洲國家錦標賽}}，認為此舉侵犯了亞巴佐尼亞的主權<ref>{{cite web|url= https://cameroonnewsagency.com/separatist-leaders-welcome-biyas-military-option-say-they-are-ready/|title= Separatist Leaders Welcome Biya’s Military Option, Say They Are Ready|publisher= Cameroon News Agency|date= 2021-01-04|accessdate= 2021-04-06|archive-date= 2021-02-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210204204558/https://cameroonnewsagency.com/separatist-leaders-welcome-biyas-military-option-say-they-are-ready/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。截至2021年3月，衝突已造成超過4000人死亡，並造成超過70萬人流離失所<ref name="aljazeeraapr12021"/>。

2019年中起宣布獨立的亞巴佐尼亞政權{{tsl|en|2019 Ambazonian leadership crisis|2009年亞巴佐尼亞政權危機|分裂成兩派}}，使局勢更形複雜<ref name="reutersjul42020">{{cite web|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-cameroon-separatists/cameroon-holds-first-peace-talks-with-main-separatist-insurgents-idUKKBN2442IW|title=Cameroon holds first peace talks with main separatist insurgents|publisher=Reuters|date=2020-07-04|accessdate=2021-04-06|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030083646/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-cameroon-separatists/cameroon-holds-first-peace-talks-with-main-separatist-insurgents-idUKKBN2442IW|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同年一些自[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]引渡回國的分離主義分子（亞巴佐尼亞第一任總統{{le|朱利葉斯·西西庫·阿尤克·塔布|Julius Sisiku Ayuk Tabe}}等人）被判死刑，但在國際壓力下喀麥隆政府在獄中與他們對話<ref name="theafricareportjul62020">{{cite web|url= https://www.theafricareport.com/32444/cameroon-government-is-secretly-negotiating-with-the-ambazonians/|title= Cameroon: Government is secretly negotiating with the Ambazonians|publisher= The Africa Report|date= 2020-07-06|accessdate= 2021-04-06|archive-date= 2021-01-25|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210125114144/https://www.theafricareport.com/32444/cameroon-government-is-secretly-negotiating-with-the-ambazonians/|dead-url= no}}</ref> 。

